{"word":"φημίζω","slug":"φημίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φημίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φήμη'><el>φήμη</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to utter a voice</i>, <el>φήμην φημίζειν</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to spread a report</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>: <i>to prophesy</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to express in words</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> also <i>to promise</i>, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}